node.text:
Me vs Clare - Whoever wins get's the incredible ASUS ROG Zephyrus Duo 15 SE laptop! 😍
 
With TWO screens, I played Fortnite on the top screen whilst Clare sent me challenges I HAD to do on the bottom. If I get a Victory Royale, the laptop's mine, if I don't, Clare gets it! 🔥
 
Find out who won by clicking the link in my bio - Go watch it now! 👍 #ROG #ZephyrusDuo @ASUSROG #AD
